title: About
text:
Hi there! My name is Kendrick Teo, and I’m a final-year student of Singapore Management University (SMU).
The purpose of this website is to document my learning journey in the course: IS415: Geospatial Analytics and Applications under professor Kam Tin Seong. Follow along with my coursework below as I explore the vast world of data analytics, geospatial analytics and urban planning.
If you’re liking this site so far, I would most appreciate it if you could connect with me on LinkedIn!
